Package: mdbtoolr
Type: Package
Title: DBI Interface to 'mdbtools' for Microsoft Access Databases
Version: 0.0.0.9900
Authors@R: person("Bruno", "Tremblay", email = "bruno@boostao.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Bruno Tremblay [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Bruno Tremblay <bruno@boostao.ca>
Description: Provides a read-only DBI backend and high-level helper
    functions for Microsoft Access '.mdb' and '.accdb' files. Uses
    vendored native 'mdbtools' library sources compiled into the package,
    so core functionality does not require external 'mdbtools' command-line
    tools at runtime.
License: GPL-2 | LGPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Depends: R (>= 4.1)
Imports:
    DBI,
    methods,
    utils,
    jsonlite
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
SystemRequirements: GNU make
NeedsCompilation: yes
Config/testthat/edition: 3
URL: https://github.com/boostao/mdbtoolr/, https://github.com/mdbtools/mdbtools/
BugReports: https://github.com/boostao/mdbtoolr/issues
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
